title: Presidio of San Francisco: Guided Tours
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Things To Do     Guided Tours              Guided Tours          The National Park Service at the Presidio offers a variety of scheduled ranger and docent led programs.  Groups visiting the park may also arrange ranger-led programs by appointment in advance. Availability subject to staffing levels. Please allow at least 3-weeks advance notice. To schedule a group program contact Presidio Interpretation at (415) 561-2817 or (415) 561-4323.
